<!doctype html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <title><%= subject %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: gray;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div style="background-color: white; width: 100%; height: auto;">
      <br>
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dw80q5cqf/image/upload/v1743435062/D95879A1-F3BF-4EF9-883F-CFBFD8C5EE8A_4_5005_c-removebg-preview_o7b0k7.png" alt="Image" width="30%" style="height: auto;" />
      </p>
    </div>
    <h2>Dear <%= firstName %>,</h2>
    <p>
      We recently detected unusual activity on your account.
      To protect your account, we have temporarily restricted access until further verification.
    </p>
    <p>
      Please visit your account dashboard to complete the security verification process.
      This will ensure the continued safety of your account.
    </p>
    <p>If you did not initiate this request, please contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:support@ntbank.org">support@ntbank.org</a>.</p>

    <p>Thank you for choosing National Trust Bank. We are here to assist you anytime.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>National Trust Bank Care - Always By Your Side</p>
      <p>Don't want to receive these emails? <a href="#">Unsubscribe</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>